title: Division Winners, Wild Card Teams, and a Super Bowl Champion | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
The Ringer’s Kevin Clark is joined by Nora Princiotti, Kaelen Jones, and Danny Kelly to pick division winners (3:48), which teams will get the wild-card spots (66:06), and a Super Bowl champion (69:17). 
Host: Kevin Clark 
Guest: Nora Princiotti, Kaelen Jones, and Danny Kelly
